# Legacy entrypoint — rules live under `.cursor/rules/`

Cursor loads project rules from **`.cursor/rules/*.mdc`**.

- **`gpxmapper-core.mdc`** — always applied (project + workflow)
- **`python-standards.mdc`** — Python files (`**/*.py`)
- **`git-github-workflow.mdc`** — always applied (commits, branches, PRs)

Do not duplicate long policy here; edit the `.mdc` files instead.
